download with git

    git clone git://github.com/genjix/kio.git

install python 3

    sudo aptitude install python3

copy eodict to /usr/share/
set permissions on kio to be executable
copy kio to /usr/bin

    sudo cp eodict /usr/local/share
    sudo chmod +x kio
    sudo cp kio /usr/local/bin

now you can run

    kio vetero
    kio weather

the x-system and letters themselves work interchangeably

    kio mangxi
    kio manƒùi

the dictionary file is from http://www.esperanto-panorama.net/vortaro/eoen.htm
